-- This is the BOOTSTRAP MOMENT. Zero domain cells exist. The meta-cell
-- must decide from scratch what processing is needed.

вҠў analyze-problem
  given problemвҶ’statement вүЎ "Plan a weekend trip to Tokyo for someone who loves ramen and architecture."
  yield needed-cells[], rationale

-- LLM evaluation:

  yield needed-cells вүЎ [
    {
      name: "research-ramen",
      type: "research",
      purpose: "Find the best ramen restaurants in Tokyo, covering different styles (tonkotsu, shoyu, miso, tsukemen) and neighborhoods.",
      inputs: "none",
      outputs: "ramen-spots[]"
    },
    {
      name: "research-architecture",
      type: "research",
      purpose: "Identify notable architectural landmarks in Tokyo вҖ” traditional temples, modern skyscrapers, famous buildings by renowned architects (Ando, Kuma, Tange).",
      inputs: "none",
      outputs: "architecture-spots[]"
    },
    {
      name: "research-logistics",
      type: "research",
      purpose: "Gather practical info: Tokyo transit system (Suica card, JR lines, Metro), typical costs, neighborhood geography, weekend timing considerations.",
      inputs: "none",
      outputs: "logistics-info"
    },
    {
      name: "plan-day-saturday",
      type: "planning",
      purpose: "Build Saturday itinerary combining ramen and architecture spots with transit routing.",
      inputs: "research-ramenвҶ’ramen-spots, research-architectureвҶ’architecture-spots, research-logisticsвҶ’logistics-info",
      outputs: "saturday-plan"
    },
    {
      name: "plan-day-sunday",
      type: "planning",
      purpose: "Build Sunday itinerary for remaining spots, with different neighborhood focus than Saturday.",
      inputs: "research-ramenвҶ’ramen-spots, research-architectureвҶ’architecture-spots, research-logisticsвҶ’logistics-info, plan-day-saturdayвҶ’saturday-plan",
      outputs: "sunday-plan"
    },
    {
      name: "synthesize-itinerary",
      type: "synthesis",
      purpose: "Combine both days into a complete weekend itinerary with practical tips, budget estimate, and alternatives.",
      inputs: "plan-day-saturdayвҶ’saturday-plan, plan-day-sundayвҶ’sunday-plan, research-logisticsвҶ’logistics-info",
      outputs: "full-itinerary"
    }
  ]

  yield rationale вүЎ "The problem requires three research streams (ramen, architecture, logistics) that can run in parallel вҖ” these are root cells with no dependencies. Two planning cells sequence the days (Sunday depends on Saturday to avoid duplication). One synthesis cell combines everything. This gives complete coverage: what to see, what to eat, how to get around, and practical details."

-- oracle checks:
--   вҠЁ length(needed-cells) вүҘ 3 вҶ’ вң“ (6 cells)
--   вҠЁ needed-cells includes at least one research cell вҶ’ вң“ (3 research cells)
--   вҠЁ needed-cells includes at least one synthesis cell вҶ’ вң“ (synthesize-itinerary)
--   вҠЁ needed-cells dataflow forms a DAG вҶ’ вң“
--     research-ramen, research-architecture, research-logistics (roots)
--     вҶ’ plan-day-saturday вҶ’ plan-day-sunday вҶ’ synthesize-itinerary
--   вҠЁ needed-cells collectively address the full problem вҶ’ вң“
--     ramen вң“, architecture вң“, logistics вң“, both days вң“, integration вң“

